
how to start with tailwind frame work css

1. npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer vite run

2. npx tailwindcss init -p run

3. in tailwind.config.js put star * in content

4. in package.json add "scripts":{"start":"vite"},

5. create main.css and copy three lines
@tailwind base
@tailwind components
@tailwind utilities

6. link main.css in index.html

7. add fonts in main.css (if any)

8. in config.js, add font family after plugins

9. got to view terminal and write npm run start

10. follow link cmd+click






